DCR MassParks Pass (Department of Conservation and Recreation)- Entitles the bearer to FREE parking for one vehicle (excluding vans or buses) at Massachusetts parks.&nbsp;
Pick up and return to library.
Pass may be picked up the day before use.&nbsp;
Pass must be returned no later than the day after use.
Pass allows 1 car and up to 9 passengers into the state park or beach.&nbsp;
Pass is for day use only and CANNOT be used for camping.&nbsp;

